Package: pmxSynthData
Title: Differentially Private Mock Pharmacometric Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Andrew", "Stein", , "andy.stein@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fits a low-dimensional subject-level differentially private
    population generator to pharmacometric event data, then creates
    structurally coherent mock data for model-workflow exploration by
    post-processing the fitted model. The generator uses explicit public
    domains and contribution limits, supports endpoint-specific scientific
    clocks and censoring conventions, and does not copy source patient event
    templates or fit a pharmacokinetic, pharmacodynamic, or nonlinear
    mixed-effects model.
